Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.48,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,何これー
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.48,0:02:25.09,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃん大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.09,0:02:28.73,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,これきっとさっきのちっちゃいのにやられたんだよ　きっと
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.73,0:02:29.83,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,生きてる
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.83,0:02:31.62,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,全然　とれない
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.62,0:02:32.83,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留ちゃんは
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.00,0:02:37.91,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,駄目
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.91,0:02:40.97,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,てかものすごく撃たれたよね　ミサイルっぽいのも
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.27,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ポインじゃなくて　ミサイル　ミサイル
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.27,0:02:45.06,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,それ以外も　ミニミニソルジャーが
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.97,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,バンバン撃ってきた　痛がゆいの
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.97,0:02:48.16,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,きっとあれだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.74,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ちっちゃいから　威力もちっちゃいいんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.74,0:02:51.55,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そうなの
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.55,0:02:52.68,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,わからん　たぶん
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.68,0:02:55.07,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,それより　これどんなきゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.28,0:02:55.81,JP-Main-up-8,Shizuru,0,0,0,,そうだ　そうだね
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.81,0:02:58.61,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ああ　もう
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.05,0:03:16.01,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,お前たち　一体何者だ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.89,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,まず　これとって
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.89,0:03:18.70,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,答えろ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.08,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,やだ　とったら話す
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.30,0:03:23.59,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,ならば　死ぬまでそうしているがいい
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.74,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吾野から来たぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.57,0:03:28.82,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,吾野
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.38,0:03:31.84,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,吾野の人間も　変わっていないのか
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.84,0:03:33.91,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,も　もって
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.91,0:03:36.84,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,吾野は皆以前のままなのかと聞いている
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.84,0:03:40.18,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私たちはまだだけど　動物ならそのうち
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.45,0:03:41.99,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,ここへは　何しに来た
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.58,0:03:44.68,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,散歩に
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.15,0:03:45.77,JP-Main-up-8,Reimi,0,0,0,,お医者さん探してんの
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.77,0:03:46.99,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,なんで言うの
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.10,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,言うんじゃないの
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.88,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ちょっとずつ言おうと思ったのに
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.88,0:03:51.47,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,そんなん知らないもん
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.47,0:03:53.82,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,全部言っちゃったら　駆け引きできないじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.83,0:03:56.00,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,え　これ取ったら話すって　私言ったよ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.92,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,それでおっさんかえろとしたじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.92,0:04:00.40,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,最初から　あの態度じゃ駄目なんだって
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.40,0:04:02.02,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,おっさんムカつくんだもん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.02,0:04:04.43,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,私だってムカつくよ　こんなおっさん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.37,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,回せー
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.35,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,何々
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.02,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ちょちょちょっ　痛っ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.62,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ちょっとやめて
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.23,JP-Main-up-8,Shizuru,0,0,0,,痛っ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.62,0:04:18.23,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,顔痛いって
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.23,0:04:18.99,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,止めろ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.90,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,うるさいんだよ　お前ら
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.88,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,今こっちが質問してんだろうが
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.88,0:04:26.44,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,勝手に喧嘩してるんじゃないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.44,0:04:28.29,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,喧嘩つうか　俺の悪口か
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.29,0:04:29.49,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,急にめっちゃキレて
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.49,0:04:30.49,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,キレてないわ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.49,0:04:32.13,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,誰が小娘相手にキレるか
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.13,0:04:33.32,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,隊長だぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.32,0:04:35.03,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,なんで隊長が小娘相手に
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.03,0:04:35.50,JP-Main-Down,Soldier,0,0,0,,隊長
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.94,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,わかってるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.30,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,医者を探すと言ったが　吾野にもいるだろ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.54,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ドクターって人探してる
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.33,0:04:45.82,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,なぜドクターを
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.82,0:04:47.22,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,友達に茸生えて
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.66,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,抜いちゃったから死んじゃうかもしんないの
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.66,0:04:50.73,JP-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,茸
