Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.89,0:21:16.76,JP-Main-up-8,Boss,0,0,0,,下ろせ　下ろせよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.18,0:21:15.50,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,あれどこ行くの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.50,0:21:19.24,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,7Gで馬鹿でかくなったさやまこに無人島ができてな
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.24,0:21:21.34,JP-Main-up-8,Boss,0,0,0,,下ろせ来て
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.57,0:21:21.33,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,あそこならそうそう出られない
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.34,0:21:25.22,JP-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,あんな何もねえとこやだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.22,0:21:27.65,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,私は善治郎のもとへ向かう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.65,0:21:30.42,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,この状況を良くする方法が見つかるかもしれん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.68,0:21:31.99,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,でもここは
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.99,0:21:34.69,JP-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,私たちで自警団を作ることになりました
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.69,0:21:37.30,JP-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,ああそっか　武器あるし
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.30,0:21:39.55,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,ドクター私らと逆向きの旅だね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.55,0:21:41.07,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,このサイズだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.07,0:21:44.15,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,車にありったけの燃料を積んでも何日かかるか
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.41,0:21:47.04,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,気をつけて　何あるかわかんないし
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.04,0:21:48.37,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,それは私らもだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.37,0:21:51.50,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,目的地への道のりとはそういうものだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.50,0:21:52.74,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,だからこそ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.74,0:21:55.08,JP-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,一歩を踏み出す勇気には価値がある
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.69,0:22:05.14,JP-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,ブレースレット　また作ったけ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.14,0:22:06.37,JP-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,本当
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.29,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,OP前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.29,0:00:03.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,學習到底是為了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.91,0:00:05.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,一點也不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.32,0:00:08.69,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,正是因為不懂才去學習的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:12.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,葉香有時候也說些理解不能的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:22.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留你許了什麼願望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:23.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:24.72,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你許了什麼願呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:25.36,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:26.24,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:36.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,上啊 撫子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.07,0:00:38.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,打倒對方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.52,0:00:42.39,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,去啊 戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:43.29,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:45.03,ZH-Main-Down,Yoka,0,0,0,,打倒對方
Comment: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:21.87,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:25.09,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:28.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這肯定是剛才那群小人搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:29.83,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:31.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,完全掙不開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:32.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:37.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:40.97,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,話說他們發射了很多東西 比如導彈什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是什麼點 是導彈 是導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:45.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,除此之外 還有迷你士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.97,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,砰砰朝我們開槍 痛不欲生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:48.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,肯定就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.74,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但因為質量很小 所以威力也不大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.74,0:02:51.55,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:52.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不知道 大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:55.07,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,比起這個 繩子呀怎麼解開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:55.81,ZH-Main-up-8,Shizuru,0,0,0,,對 確實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:58.61,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:16.01,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,你們倆 到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.89,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,首先 把我們放開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:18.70,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,回答我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不要 放開我再說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:23.59,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,那麼 到你死之前都可以保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們從吾野來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:28.82,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:31.84,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,吾野的人 也沒有任何變化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:33.91,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也 再說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:36.84,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我是問 吾野的大家是否還和以前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:40.18,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們雖然沒有 但遲早會變成動物的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:41.99,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,你們來這裡 做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:44.68,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,散步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:45.77,ZH-Main-up-8,Reimi,0,0,0,,我們在找醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:46.99,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,為什麼說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.10,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,難道不說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,本來想一點點說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:51.47,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你這樣我又不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:53.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,全部都說出來 討價還價的份都沒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:56.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 讓他們放開後再說話 我不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.92,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你這樣子大叔一點變通的餘地都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:00.40,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,最開始 你那種態度就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:02.02,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,可是大叔我好不爽他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:04.43,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我也好不爽啊 這臭男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.37,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,轉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什麼什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.02,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等等等會 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,快點停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.23,ZH-Main-up-8,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:18.23,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,臉也好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:18.99,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,停止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.90,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,好吵啊 你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.88,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,現在是我在質問你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:26.44,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,別自顧自就拌起嘴來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:28.29,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,你倆吵架 卻說我壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:29.49,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,突然非常火大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:30.49,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我才沒火大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:32.13,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,誰會跟一個小女孩發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:33.32,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我可是隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:35.03,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,為什麼隊長要對一個小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:35.50,ZH-Main-Down,Soldier,0,0,0,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.94,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.30,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,你們說你們要找醫生 吾野應該也有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我們在找刀客塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:45.82,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,為什麼找刀客塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:47.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我的朋友長了蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,雖然拔下來了 但是很可能快要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:50.73,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:52.62,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,那也是7G影響造成的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:55.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,肯定是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:56.68,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,絕對是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:59.39,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,果然 老闆說的是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什麼情況 剛剛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.76,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我們立刻向上級匯報
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:03.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:05.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,話都說完了放我們下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.02,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我並未做出過這樣的承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:09.92,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,我們不能向外部來者洩露城市的資訊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:10.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:13.57,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,這是我們「英明」的老闆做的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:14.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:17.68,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,奉老闆之命 明天 你們的骨架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:20.79,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,將會在狹山市立博物館的曙光劍齒象骨架旁展出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.05,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,骨架是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:23.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,變成骨架的話說明已經死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.32,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是死刑啊 這
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:27.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等會 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:30.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,放開我 你這豌豆大小的垃圾蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:32.65,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,電流正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:33.77,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,電壓正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:34.35,ZH-Main-up-8,Akira,0,0,0,,撫子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:36.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,安東尼 快點過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:38.92,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.31,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,波奇 小晶她叫我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:43.64,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,快點過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:44.28,ZH-Main-up-8,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好好好行行行 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:46.41,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小晶 怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:49.76,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲實和靜留 她們倆去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:52.48,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,小晶一個人好孤獨好無聊噗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.53,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:56.09,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,她們肯定很快就回來的 再稍微等等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:59.59,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,她們兩人絕對會繞行 去偷吃米飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:02.50,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,所以我也要和安東尼一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:06.33,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,波奇 檢查結束前就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:10.42,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,安東尼 毛茸茸的好可愛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:13.68,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你的臉越來越變得可愛了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:16.31,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊敲 手好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:18.04,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,別這樣 會出血的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.87,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,現在不是說這個的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:21.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,手鍊可是會斷掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:24.05,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,聽聽我的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:24.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:27.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,已經知道這個城鎮裡確實有個很好的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:28.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:30.02,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,還有就是要找到對方 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:30.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,解開這個的方法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:33.33,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這個還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.03,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那這
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:35.55,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這件事才是最重要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:37.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,期望越高 失望越大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:40.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的是 難道就沒好辦法了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:43.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等會等會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:45.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等一下 大姐姐等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:47.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,拜託你幫我們鬆綁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:50.43,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們並沒有傷害你的意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:53.68,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們只是想找刀客塔 讓其幫助我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.14,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,要是和你們說話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.84,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,老闆會把我剝成骨架 然後展出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:00.58,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以那個老闆是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.59,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,回答的話也會被做成骨架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:04.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那你根本不用靠近過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:06.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,難道你有理由必須這麼做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:10.75,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,我是這裡的清潔工 負責清掃垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:13.15,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,要是不乾淨 也會被製成骨辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:13.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:15.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我們也和你一起撿垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:16.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:17.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:20.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我想放水 就在這
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,剛剛就想要去上廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:26.31,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,現在我忍不住了 要在這噓噓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:29.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,把公園搞髒也是沒辦法的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也想要屙尿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:32.63,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,會把一切搞亂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:33.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,咱可不管呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.20,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如果你給我們鬆綁 我們絕對會搞定老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:39.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留的吾野柔術可是真的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.94,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也是了不得的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:43.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,要嘛幫我 要嘛骨辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:45.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,或者被尿一身 然後被做成骨架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:46.87,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你選
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.93,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 馬上要出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:51.90,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,謝謝姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.09,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:53.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:55.09,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,去幹掉老闆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:56.71,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是先去看看刀客塔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:07:59.94,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,博士她 被老闆拘留了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.45,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:04.92,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,所以首先 要求助於知曉博士藏身之地的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.45,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,都沒人在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:08.53,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,畢竟有外出禁止令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:10.93,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以 刀客塔為什麼被拘留呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:13.35,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,這要從頭開始講起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:18.17,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,我們大家的變化 聽說高機率是7G事件所造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:22.19,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,城市不斷膨脹 然後突然逆向變得非常小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:25.39,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,在這其中 有一個居民將我們團結了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:26.61,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,那就是博士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.67,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,戈帕·誠·安斯特朗姆女士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:30.35,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好強 無論工作還是名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:32.82,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,大家推舉誠老師為領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:36.48,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,除了大小以外 生活水準基本維持不變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:39.58,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,但是就在這時 老闆出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.01,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,老闆很快就支配了這座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:44.41,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,因為是領袖 便抓捕了誠老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:46.15,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,然後把她監禁在某個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:47.84,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,老闆這麼厲害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:49.21,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,最後居民們被分為
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:52.00,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,服從老闆的 即上等稻荷山市民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:55.81,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,自由被剝奪的 下等稻荷山市民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:59.43,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,我們是下等稻荷山市民 全部都在管理之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.94,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,完全是為了依靠基礎設施而生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:03.87,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,基建和的中藥煎藥陶罐是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.71,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,這座城市中基地的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:08.41,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,都是為了滿足老闆的癖好而強迫人為愛發電
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:09.76,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這樣太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:11.87,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,大家都放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:14.52,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,但是 要是誠老師能夠回來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:16.91,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,或許能再一次 挺直腰板子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,因此我們才在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:19.36,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:26.58,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留 怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:45.72,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:48.05,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,請告訴我們誠老師所在的位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:50.35,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,作為曾經的上等市民 你們應該知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:56.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,情報源絕對不要暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:57.18,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.09,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,現在在稻荷山公園
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,正在尋找醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:03.08,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,為什麼要去找醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:03.71,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,生病了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:04.42,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:06.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是已經說過 小晶身上長了蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:08.19,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我知道蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.20,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,醫生什麼的我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:11.95,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稻荷山這應該有個醫生在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:12.91,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:15.85,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不是的 吧吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,撫子姐是不是有困難了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:19.82,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我的臉寫滿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:22.76,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,實際上 小晶我也是問題少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:25.68,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,身體逐漸扭曲變形動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:25.68,ZH-Main-up-8,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:27.83,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是不用擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:31.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,咱要是有困難 無論何時玲實她都會來幫我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:35.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這可是讓我肚子疼了好久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:37.23,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我沒想到你真的會去「吃書」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:39.55,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,教科書已經用不了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:40.59,ZH-Main-up-8,Akira,0,0,0,,是你把它撕爛吃掉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:42.09,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我要和你絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:43.19,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,哼 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:45.54,ZH-Main-Down,Boy A,0,0,0,,喂 你看什麼書
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.55,ZH-Main-Down,Boy B,0,0,0,,敲 好無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:48.62,ZH-Main-Down,Boy B,0,0,0,,全都是漢字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.24,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我覺得很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:51.01,ZH-Main-Down,Boy C,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:54.34,ZH-Main-Down,Boy C,0,0,0,,你就想取笑西吾野在秩父線上而不在西武池袋線上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:57.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,喂 你這群傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:00.64,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,對小晶做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:03.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但是今天稍微晚了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:06.82,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,回來之後要好好說她 笨得跟豬一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:07.43,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:08.37,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.57,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那我也一起說教說教她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:12.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,請務必這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:45.69,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,誠老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:47.89,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,山田 她們是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:48.84,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,之後再聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:49.90,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我們來幫助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:03.14,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你們這群人 在我的基地裡想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:03.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:04.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不如說挺普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:07.14,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,你們怎麼跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:08.46,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,才不告訴你 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:10.29,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你再擅自模仿他們試試
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.96,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我會把你頭拔掉 弄得你亂七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,自作主張的人是你才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:15.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我全都聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:17.46,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,等 好近 你想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:20.21,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我原本想為什麼大家要遵從你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:21.72,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,原來只是體型較大而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:23.85,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,既然知道就別說出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:26.42,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,老子最討厭的就是蠢蠢活著的辣妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:28.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,老娘也是超級討厭像你這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:29.80,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,不是 你這
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:31.87,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我比你更加更加更加討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:33.21,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你 快 摸什麼魚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:34.56,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,快點攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:35.43,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:37.07,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:39.26,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這點傷痛算不了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:40.47,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:42.36,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,核水導彈發射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:44.17,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,咪西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:45.99,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,才不會上兩次當
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.83,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,好 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:50.61,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你們是想赦免博士 然後占領這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:51.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.42,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我絕對不會讓你得逞的 笨蛋辣妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:54.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你難道是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:55.44,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.01,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:01.99,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這裡交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:02.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你先去小晶那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:03.20,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:03.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:05.08,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,發什麼呆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:06.72,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,快點向博士攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.30,ZH-Main-Down,Captain,0,0,0,,攻擊多次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:10.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:13.60,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,別讓她跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.36,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,攻擊攻擊攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.21,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:29.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:31.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,動作小玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:32.29,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,欸 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.10,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,她們是稻荷山公園的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等救治好小晶 我馬上去幫靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:37.77,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留她 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:38.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,快看小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:39.75,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,醫生來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.83,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,等會 我不是醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:42.30,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你不是刀客塔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:45.20,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,我是科學家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.24,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那完全沒用啊 你治不好她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.02,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,總而言之先告訴我發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:52.42,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,有什麼意義啊 你又不是醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:55.58,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,之前 她的屁股上長了蘑菇 拔掉之後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:56.93,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就好像變成其他人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:59.27,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,身體越來越無法動彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:00.37,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:04.60,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,晶小姐你描述一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:07.92,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,蘑菇拔出後身體除了變得沉重以外有沒其它的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:10.19,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯 我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:12.75,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,腦袋裡像是有風呼呼吹過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:14.29,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,你們真的非常幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.45,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,如果是7G的原因 醫生根本治不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,老師您能治好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:19.11,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,別急
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:21.06,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,就算是科學家 研究的領域也有區分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:24.67,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,但是我參與了7G的研究 大概能推測出一二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:25.09,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.71,ZH-Main-Down,Lady,0,0,0,,老師您參與了7G
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:29.02,ZH-Main-Down,Man,0,0,0,,那麼老闆推翻博士您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:33.32,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,他們知道我的經歷 以為這能夠讓城市恢復如初
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.89,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,我們認為當前所發生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:38.27,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,是被稱為「7G腦波干涉」的現象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:39.97,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,7-11 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:41.77,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,在7G的影響下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:45.46,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,人類的身體也會隨著意識的認知發生變化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:46.97,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,要是想要恢復如初
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:48.15,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,說得更加明白點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:50.30,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,也就是說 晶小姐的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:54.20,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,是因為意識到自己某些重要的東西和蘑菇一起被帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:56.59,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,那麼如果把「思想」給加回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:58.05,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,吃點蘑菇或許會好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:14:58.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:00.90,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,蘑菇 你們沒帶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:02.03,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:03.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,還要去東吾野嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:06.62,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,不用 我記得老闆的屋裡長的有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:07.25,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,蘑菇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:09.34,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,如果善治郎還活著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:11.63,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,或許我們能夠採取更好的應對方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:13.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 善治郎的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:16.23,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是吾野的 平善治郎先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:17.59,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,你們為什麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:19.08,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,那傢伙還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:21.47,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,還活著 但是變成搞笑擔當了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:24.20,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeko,0,0,0,,善治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.78,ZH-Main-Down,Pontaro,0,0,0,,軟綿綿 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.15,ZH-Main-Down,Surgeon,0,0,0,,軟綿綿手術 準備開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:43.60,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:46.39,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,別站這裡 繼續走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:47.82,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,快點走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:54.47,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,善治郎是我的恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:57.42,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,總而言之現在最重要是晶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:06.48,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這裡是 哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.22,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,俺的房間呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:10.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你打算幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:11.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,判我死刑拿我骨頭去裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:14.29,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,確實 這也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:17.40,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我還能動的時候 可是不會覺得自己輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:19.10,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,對 確實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:21.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,為什麼要做這些事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:24.54,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你這樣只是恃強凌弱罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:28.45,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,基地 我喜歡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:29.29,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:30.39,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,很帥是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:33.60,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,戰鬥機 直升機 還有各式各樣的車
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:37.01,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我雖然一直都很憧憬 但從未和別人提起過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:39.91,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,但我最初的時候也交到了一些朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:42.59,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,我說也想和他們一樣在基地裡工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:44.42,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,然後就被笑爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:47.55,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,他們說 以你的頭腦和運動神經當然是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:53.36,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,然後7G發生後 就來到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:57.20,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,反正那群人只會認為你無聊至極瘋狂愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:16:59.22,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:00.89,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,為什麼你看起來這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.19,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,唔 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:06.14,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋 你有去過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:06.60,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.18,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你要去池袋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:09.67,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,那裡很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:12.42,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,比起在那個鬼地方 和我在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:13.42,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,行 行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:15.87,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,順帶一提
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:19.84,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,如果你能留在這裡 就放你的朋友走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:27.68,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留和蘑菇交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:30.68,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,都說了我最討厭辣妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:37.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是時候放棄你的想法吧 矮窮挫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:38.44,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,閉嘴閉嘴閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:39.29,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,可惡的辣妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:41.76,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,俺的基地絕對不會讓給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:57.33,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:14.08,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.96,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,教科書 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:17.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:18.98,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:24.59,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,目標命中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:25.14,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:26.46,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,那樣子的話可糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:28.92,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,確實 糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:30.59,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.72,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,等等等等會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:37.75,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,你們這群笨蛋 快點幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:39.21,ZH-Main-Down,Boss,0,0,0,,快點幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:51.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:52.97,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.69,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:05.40,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:06.79,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,已經吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:08.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,笨笨笨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:10.77,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:11.51,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.89,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話小晶她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這根本 不是小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:22.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,憤世嫉俗 晦澀難懂的這些傻瓜書籍沒有被讀過的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:25.11,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那本書是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:28.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這是你的 最喜歡東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:33.09,ZH-Main-up-8,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:31.25,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,最喜歡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:32.71,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 等等等會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:33.65,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:33.65,ZH-Main-up-8,Makoto,0,0,0,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:34.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:35.78,ZH-Main-Down,Makoto,0,0,0,,或許這樣會有效
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:38.76,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那個時候咱原紙奉還
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:43.55,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你幹什麼鬼笨蛋玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:44.69,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:46.05,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你是虐待狂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:46.49,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,虐待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:47.46,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,薩德主義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:48.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,說白了就是性虐待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:50.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,對他人的身體施加虐待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.31,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,在對對方全身造成痛苦的過程中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:54.08,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,享受性興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:55.96,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你不懂就去讀薩德侯爵的書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:58.70,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但這對笨蛋來說根本看不懂罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:00.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:02.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我的龍彥
